				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "One liner for GondianWorker_PostIRN01, who only comes on stage if at least 2 workroom gondians are dead when the player returns from the Iron Throne. This gondian has helped the player kill the banites and is now afraid of what the consequences will be. The Gondians thinks they never should have fought back."
